<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sakmel deihum pun lungdeih te,
 Gam lopi tuol a leng ui;
 Na leisiet hinkhuo a beih tieng,
 Nawp kiemlo in na pawl dem?

[V2]
 Guol lungtuok kikhen a um dem?
 Dantak leh, dantak leh;
 Gam nuomzaw ei na ngak achun,
 Thangvan ah, thangvah ah.

[V3]
 2. Naupang lungmawl ka hih laia,
 Hehpihmak thu ei hilh te;
 Hukdampa thihna chanchin thu,
 Tun Amah kawm a tung tau.

[V4]
 3. Na naupan laia na lasak,
 Van lam la na hezing hi;
 Ziechuh lunggil in na deih em?
 Lei chung la na tel zaw dem?

[V5]
 4. I lungdeih teu tawh I lenlai,
 Ka thilin ka mui mit tha'n;
 Kikhenna ni a hungtun in,
 Gimthei kei ei nusieh tau.

[V6]
 5. Kipak nunnuom a cheng khawm haw,
 Khat khatin a kiem zel ui;
 Lei hi kikhen na gam ahi,
 Kimna gam a um kit dem?</lyrics>
<title>WILL THE CIRCLE BE UNBROKEN?</title>
<hymn_number>387</hymn_number>
</song>